                            <ion-icon class="program-icon" name="star-outline"></ion-icon>
                            <span><strong>4.9</strong> rating (537)</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="program">
                <img src="~/Content/img/countries/australia.jpg"
                     class="program-img"
                     alt="Australia" />
                <div class="program-content">
                    <div class="program-tags">
                        <span class="tag tag--tag1">Sydney</span>
                        <span class="tag tag--tag2">Western</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="program-title">Australia</p>
                    <ul class="program-attributes">
                        <li class="program-attribute">
                            <ion-icon class="program-icon" name="star-outline"></ion-icon>
                            <span><strong>4.8</strong> rating (441)</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>


            <div class="program">
                <img src="~/Content/img/countries/england.jpg"
                     class="program-img"
                     alt="England" />
                <div class="program-content">
                    <div class="program-tags">
                        <span class="tag tag--tag1">Oxford</span>
                        <span class="tag tag--tag2">Cambridge</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="program-title">England</p>
                    <ul class="program-attributes">
                        <li class="program-attribute">
                            <ion-icon class="program-icon" name="star-outline"></ion-icon>
                            <span><strong>4.8</strong> rating (441)</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

        <div class="container all-programs">
            <a href="#" class="link">See all programs &rarr;</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-responses" id="response">
        <div class="responses-container">
            <span class="subheading">Response from students</span>
            <h2 class="heading-secondary">99% complements from the students in over the world </h2>

            <div class="responses">
                <figure class="response">
                    <img class="response-img"
                         alt="Photo of customer Dave Bryson"
                         src="~/Content/img/customers/dave.jpg" />
                    <blockquote class="response-text">
                        I know Omni is the official representative of UTS through a school conference. My application process was very smooth and fast. Thank you so much Omni and Mr. Ted.
                    </blockquote>
                    <p class="response-name">&mdash; Dave Bryson</p>
                </figure>

                <figure class="response">
                    <img class="response-img"
                         alt="Photo of customer Ben Hadley"
                         src="~/Content/img/customers/ben.jpg" />
                    <blockquote class="response-text">
                        I went to many centers, but they said 100% scholarship is difficult to get, centers told me to only get 30% maximum. When they came to Omni, the sisters did not say so, but they introduced schools with 30%, 50%, 100% scholarships. The sisters did not discourage me, but they said the conditions and requirements to win the scholarship were quite competitive, but still encouraged me to apply, and it didn't cost anything. That's what makes me feel that Omni is so different from other centers. I would like to thank Ms. Thao and Omni company for enthusiastically helping and supporting me in the process of applying and applying for scholarships.
                    </blockquote>
                    <p class="response-name">&mdash; Ben Hadley</p>
                </figure>

                <figure class="response">
                    <img class="response-img"
                         alt="Photo of customer Steve Miller"
                         src="~/Content/img/customers/steve.jpg" />
                    <blockquote class="response-text">
                        Everyone in Omni works very dedicated, I need whatever everyone helps with. The difficulties in the information, what I do not understand are answered by Ms. Aldrin very fully and in detail. From there, it helps me identify the school as well as the scholarship requirements. I thank Ms. Aldrin and Omni for helping me from the beginning of my research to completing the application as well as applying for scholarships and visas."
                    </blockquote>
                    <p class="response-name">&mdash; Steve Miller</p>
                </figure>

                <figure class="response">
                    <img class="response-img"
                         alt="Photo of customer Hannah Smith"
                         src="~/Content/img/customers/hannah.jpg" />
                    <blockquote class="response-text">
                        I am very impressed with the scholarship and school selection information that Omni provides during the counseling process, helping me to compare before making a decision that is most suitable for me. My visa application was also approved very quickly, without any problems.
                    </blockquote>
                    <p class="response-name">&mdash; Hannah Smith</p>
                </figure>
            </div>
        </div>

